message.body: This is crazy my love. We just got to the baltimore stop. 2 Hrs late! Guess i will just wait for ya. By the time we get to philly, wont be long til you get home
Omg!!! That's crazy!!
We were supposed to be in philly at this time. Crazy indeed...
I'm sorry love.
Is ok. I'll just take myself out to lunch when we finally get there :-p
Okie baby. Hope you get here soon!
Meee too! Enjoy work darling. Hope its nice and easy
Almost made it :) You said your moms working today right? Will go visit
Yes. She is working. Haha. I can't believe you're only just getting there. Sorry you had to be on be bus for so long.
Its ok. So tired, totally out of it the whole time so no biggy. Now time for food and then i'll head over to parking lot.
Okie dokie. Rest rest rest. What are you going to eat?
Heading to market east and will find some pizza! (Not in the train station of course...) I'll find some place on the walk.
Go to reading terminal :)
Oooo yeah. You a smarty! Always forget that place exists haha
Yeah yeah! It's around 12th at between market and arch.
Hehe i know where it is :) Just never think of it as an option ha
Well there you go! But brace yourself for the crowd.
Thank you, my love! And no worries. Nothing unpleasant is gonna register today hah. Too sleepy to pay any mind haha. And soon, we be together! Tis a good day :)
Yay!!!
Good choice, darling :)
Whach choose?
Deluxe white pizza with Dr. Pepper...naturally. And i may be in the mood for dessert haha. Go crazy!
Mmmmmmm
Dooo it!!
i@x@ @Oh im doing it, baby. And it hurts so good. Malt balls the size of my face haha. You should never have sent me here. Chocolate and ice cream and beautifu
i@x@ !@l honeys (the kind for eating) everywhere mmm
Haha. You're cute!
Haha no, no my love. I dont feel cute. Unless youre really into fat kids. Then im cute as a button.
I love em chunky!!
Huzzah!! Then bring on the malt balls!
:D
Whats your estimate on home time, my darling??
Dunno. Prob around 545ish?
Okie dokie :) I'll be there with yo daddy to pick ya up then. See you soon!!
Did my purse come?
I didnt see a package. Dont think so, darling. But dont you worry. Its a'comin
Hehe. Okie.
Were you sleeping?
Nope nope. Watching drama with your daddy
Oh. I thought you were whispering. Haha.
Haha kinda. Didnt want to talk over the tv. Its the final episode dun dun dunnn
HAH! You're cute.
I'm sorry we couldn't stay out. Damn cold weather.
Get home so i can kiss you. And lets stay in :)
Probably get in after 6
